-- Aspen Insurance Names Postlewhite Risk Chief as Cusack Departs
-- B y   E l i z a b e t h   B u n n
-- 2013-02-07T13:56:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-07/aspen-insurance-names-postlewhite-risk-chief-as-cusack-departs.html
Aspen Insurance Holdings Ltd. said
Julian Cusack will step down as chief risk officer effective
immediately and leave the company’s board at the annual meeting
in April.  Stephen Postlewhite, the insurer’s current head of risk,
will take over for Cusack as chief risk officer, Bermuda-based
Aspen said today in a statement distributed by Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elizabeth Bunn in New York at 
